item.title: CVE-2017-6140|2024-09-17T04:04:09.104Z -- f5%20networks%2C%20inc. -- big-ip%20ltm%2C%20aam%2C%20afm%2C%20analytics%2C%20asm%2C%20dns%2C%20gtm%2C%20pem
item.description: On the BIG-IP 2000s, 2200s, 4000s, 4200v, i5600, i5800, i7600, i7800, i10600,i10800, and VIPRION 4450 blades, running version 11.5.0, 11.5.1, 11.5.2, 11.5.3, 11.5.4, 11.6.0, 11.6.1, 12.0.0, 12.1.0, 12.1.1 or 12.1.2 of BIG-IP LTM, AAM, AFM, Analytics, ASM, DNS, GTM or PEM, an undisclosed sequence of packets sent to Virtual Servers with client or server SSL profiles may cause disruption of data plane services.
